				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: How do you do get these ARMORS?<a name="69472"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 10 04 7:53 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Allakhazam's is the best place to look for quest information on bard armor.  I assume you clicked the 'Bard Armors' link at the left and are asking about some of the sets you see there.  It's missing the GoD and OoW armors.
<br />

<br />
<u>Bard Quest Armors by Expansion</u>
<br />

<br />
<b>Omens of War</b>
<br />

<br />
Farseeker's Plate - Requires drops from raid-level mobs in the end-zone of Omens, Citadel of Anguish.
<br />

<br />
Traveler's Mail - Quested by collecting components that drop from experience group level mobs.  <a href="http://www.therunes.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=6295">Quest Description</a>.
<br />

<br />

<br />
<b>Gates of Discord</b>
<br />

<br />
Luvwen's - Quested from molds that drop in Qvic and beyond.  <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2813">Quest Description</a>
<br />

<br />

<br />
<b>Planes of Power</b>
<br />

<br />
Rizlona's - Quested from molds that drop in the Elemental planes and Plane of Time.  <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2267">Quest Description</a>
<br />

<br />
Composers - Quested from molds that drop from experience group level mobs in Tier 2+ zones.  <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2263">Quest Description</a>
<br />

<br />
Good luck.
<br />

<br />
Calli</span></td>
