				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: How do you do get these ARMORS?<a name="69521"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 11 04 1:18 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>To get the rest of the suit, I suggest finding a high elf smith who is still working on her smithing skill.  Often they're willing to trade components for pieces, so you could probably farm Essence of Moonlight in Mistmoore, get xp, and help out a smith.  Morning Dew (foraged in Faydark) is also used in the combines.  So are medium quality or better bear, cat, and wolf pelts for the leather padding, so you could also farm those and increase your chances of finding a willing smith.
<br />

<br />
Good luck!
<br />

